<br />
<b><font color="#FF0000">TCG Pet Giveaway Update</font></b> - The WoWDB winners have finally been selected. <b><a href="http://www.wowdb.com/private-messages" target="_blank">Please check your PMs on WoWDB</a></b>, we are still waiting on the last winner (username starts with "v") to reply. Thanks to <b><a href="http://www.wowtcgloot.com/" target="_blank">WoWTCGLoot</a></b> for the prizes, and look for another contest soon. <br />
<br />
<font size="3"><b>Season 13 Armor Sets Recap</b></font><br />
With all of the Season 13 sets being in game now, it is time to preview the last one and recap them all! We have seen a few of the off set pieces appear <a href="http://ptr.wowdb.com/items/armor?filter-patch=16408&amp;filter-pvp-only=y&amp;filter-quality=16&amp;filter-source=128" target="_blank">on the BMAH on the PTR</a>, so it is safe to assume that they will be sold on the BMAH once the patch is live, <a href="http://www.wowdb.com/items/armor?filter-pvp-only=y&amp;filter-quality=16&amp;filter-source=128" target="_blank">just like the current PvP gear</a>.<br />
<br />
The priest set is still missing the belt and there may be other minor issues with the sets, so keep in mind that these are just previews and not the final product. <br />
