Unlocking this stage is <a href="http://ptr.wowdb.com/quests/32593-the-thunder-forge" target="_blank">part of the 5.2 legendary quest line</a> and will allow you to being <a href="http://ptr.wowdb.com/spells/138646-lightning-steel-ingot" target="_blank">crafting</a> <b><a href="http://ptr.wowdb.com/items/94111-lightning-steel-ingot" target="_blank"><font color="#0070dd">Lightning Steel Ingots</font></a></b> for the <b><a href="http://ptr.wowdb.com/items/weapons?filter-patch=16408&amp;filter-source=2" target="_blank">new replica Blacksmith weapons</a></b>.<br />
