Meaning items that drop off "trash". Greens and blues and such. (<a href="http://blue.mmo-champion.com/topic/253724-failbag-rewards-in-52-thoughts/" target="_blank"><b>Blue Tracker</b></a> / <a href="http://us.battle.net/wow/en/forum/topic/7908331229?page=2#22" target="_blank"><b>Official Forums</b></a>)</div>
